    <title type="html"><![CDATA[OpenSolaris 安裝 Flash Player]]></title>
    <link href="http://pro.ctlok.com/2010/02/opensolaris-flash-player.html"/>
    <updated>2010-02-19T13:30:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://pro.ctlok.com/2010/02/opensolaris-flash-player</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>首先到&nbsp;<a href="http://get.adobe.com/flashplayer/">http://get.adobe.com/flashplayer/</a>&nbsp;下載最新的 Flash Player for&nbsp;Solaris。<br /><br />利用以下指令去解壓縮檔案，flash_player_10_solaris_x86.tar.bz2 這個檔案會根據 flash player 版本不同而有所變更。<br /><pre class="bash">tar -jxv -f flash_player_10_solaris_x86.tar.bz2<br /></pre><br />解壓縮後會多出一個資料夾，flash_player_10_solaris_r45_2_x86 這個資料夾會根據 flash player 版本不同而有所變更，用以下指令去將資料夾內的檔案複製到 Firefox 的 plugin 資料夾下。<br /><pre class="brush: bash">pfexec cp flash_player_10_solaris_r45_2_x86/libflashplayer.so /usr/lib/firefox/plugins/<br /></pre><br />重新啟動 Firefox，然後到:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.youtube.com/">http://www.youtube.com</a> 測試一下是否正常播放影片。<br /><br />相關書籍: <a imageanchor="1" target="_blank"  href="http://www.amazon.com/OpenSolaris-Bible-Wiley-Nicholas-Solter/dp/0470385480?ie=UTF8&tag=program06-20&link_code=bil&camp=213689&creative=392969"><img alt="OpenSolaris Bible (Bible (Wiley))" src="http://ws.amazon.com/widgets/q?MarketPlace=US&ServiceVersion=20070822&ID=AsinImage&WS=1&Format=_SL160_&ASIN=0470385480&tag=program06-20" /></a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=program06-20&l=bil&camp=213689&creative=392969&o=1&a=0470385480" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important; padding: 0px !important" /><a imageanchor="1" target="_blank"  href="http://www.amazon.com/Flash-CS4-Professional-Digital-Classroom/dp/0470410930?ie=UTF8&tag=program06-20&link_code=bil&camp=213689&creative=392969"><img alt="Flash CS4 Professional Digital Classroom" src="http://ws.amazon.com/widgets/q?MarketPlace=US&ServiceVersion=20070822&ID=AsinImage&WS=1&Format=_SL160_&ASIN=0470410930&tag=program06-20" /></a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=program06-20&l=bil&camp=213689&creative=392969&o=1&a=0470410930" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important; padding: 0px !important" /><a imageanchor="1" target="_blank"  href="http://www.amazon.com/YouTube-Video-Marketing-Hour-Day/dp/0470459697?ie=UTF8&tag=program06-20&link_code=bil&camp=213689&creative=392969"><img alt="YouTube and Video Marketing: An Hour a Day" src="http://ws.amazon.com/widgets/q?MarketPlace=US&ServiceVersion=20070822&ID=AsinImage&WS=1&Format=_SL160_&ASIN=0470459697&tag=program06-20" /></a><img src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=program06-20&l=bil&camp=213689&creative=392969&o=1&a=0470459697" width="1" height="1" border="0" alt="" style="border:none !important; margin:0px !important; padding: 0px !important" /><div class="blogger-post-footer"><img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5998578522192555089-2596734896448271512?l=lawpronotes.blogspot.com' alt='' /></div></p>
]]></content>
